{% extends 'outils/_layout.html.twig' %}
{% block title %}Équipes équilibrées — {{ classe.nom }}{% endblock %}
{% block tool_title %}⚖️ Équipes équilibrées{% endblock %}

{% block tool_body %}
<div data-controller="equipes"
     data-equipes-eleves-value="{{ elevesJson }}"
     data-equipes-classe-id-value="{{ classe.id }}">

    {# Student selection panel #}
    <div class="card border-0 shadow-sm mb-3" style="border-left: 3px solid #0f9e8e !important;">
        <div class="card-header bg-white border-0 py-2 px-3 d-flex align-items-center justify-content-between"
             style="cursor:pointer" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#eleveSelectBody">
            <span class="fw-semibold small">
                <i class="bi bi-people-fill text-primary me-1"></i>
                Élèves participants
                <span class="ms-1 text-muted fw-normal" data-equipes-target="selectCounter"></span>
            </span>
            <i class="bi bi-chevron-down text-muted small"></i>
        </div>
        <div class="collapse show" id="eleveSelectBody">
            <div class="card-body pt-1 pb-2 px-3">
                <div class="d-flex gap-2 mb-2">
                    <button class="btn btn-outline-primary btn-sm py-0" data-action="equipes#selectAll">
                        <i class="bi bi-check2-all me-1"></i>Tous
                    </button>
                    <button class="btn btn-outline-secondary btn-sm py-0" data-action="equipes#selectNone">
                        <i class="bi bi-x-lg me-1"></i>Aucun
                    </button>
                </div>
                <div data-equipes-target="eleveSelectList" class="d-flex flex-wrap"></div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    {# Config #}
    <div class="card border-0 shadow-sm mb-3">
        <div class="card-body py-2 px-3">
            <div class="row g-2 align-items-center flex-wrap">
                <div class="col-auto">
                    <label class="form-label fw-semibold mb-0 small">Nombre d'équipes</label>
                </div>
                <div class="col-auto">
                    <input type="number" class="form-control form-control-sm" style="width:80px"
                           data-equipes-target="nbEquipesInput" value="2" min="2" max="10">
                </div>
                <div class="col-auto">
                    <div class="form-check form-switch mb-0">
                        <input class="form-check-input" type="checkbox" id="mixiteCheck"
                               data-equipes-target="mixiteInput" checked>
                        <label class="form-check-label fw-semibold small" for="mixiteCheck">
                            Respecter la mixité
                        </label>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="col-auto">
                    <div class="form-check form-switch mb-0">
                        <input class="form-check-input" type="checkbox" id="niveauCheck"
                               data-equipes-target="niveauInput">
                        <label class="form-check-label fw-semibold small" for="niveauCheck">
                            Équilibrer par niveau
                        </label>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="col-auto ms-auto d-flex gap-2">
                    <button class="btn btn-primary btn-sm" data-action="equipes#generate">
                        <i class="bi bi-magic me-1"></i>Générer
                    </button>
                    <button class="btn btn-outline-secondary btn-sm" data-action="equipes#shuffle">
                        <i class="bi bi-shuffle me-1"></i>Mélanger
                    </button>
                    <button class="btn btn-outline-success btn-sm" data-action="equipes#print">
                        <i class="bi bi-printer me-1"></i>Imprimer
                    </button>
                    <button class="btn btn-success btn-sm" data-action="equipes#save">
                        <i class="bi bi-cloud-upload-fill me-1"></i>Sauvegarder
                    </button>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    {# Niveau legend #}
    <div class="d-flex gap-2 flex-wrap mb-2 px-1 small text-muted align-items-center">
        <span class="fw-semibold">Niveaux :</span>
        <span><span class="badge bg-danger">1</span> Faible</span>
        <span><span class="badge bg-warning text-dark">2</span> Moyen −</span>
        <span><span class="badge bg-info text-dark">3</span> Moyen</span>
        <span><span class="badge bg-primary">4</span> Moyen +</span>
        <span><span class="badge bg-success">5</span> Fort</span>
        <span class="ms-2"><a href="{{ path('app_classe_show', {id: classe.id}) }}" class="text-muted">
            <i class="bi bi-pencil-square me-1"></i>Modifier les niveaux dans la fiche classe
        </a></span>
    </div>

    {# Info #}
    <div class="alert alert-info border-0 py-2 small" data-equipes-target="infoText" style="display:none">
        <i class="bi bi-info-circle me-1"></i>
        <span data-equipes-target="infoContent"></span>
    </div>

    {# Teams display #}
    <div class="row g-3" data-equipes-target="equipesDisplay">
        <div class="col-12 text-center text-muted py-5">
            <div class="fs-1 mb-2">⚖️</div>
            <p>Configurez le nombre d'équipes et cliquez sur <strong>Générer</strong>.</p>
        </div>
    </div>

    {# Swap instruction #}
    <div class="text-center text-muted small mt-2" data-equipes-target="swapHint" style="display:none">
        <i class="bi bi-arrows-move me-1"></i>Cliquez sur un élève pour le sélectionner, puis cliquez sur un autre pour les échanger.
    </div>
</div>
{% endblock %}
